{"tid":2330425,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大專生藏六角匙判入更生中心 鄭念慈以近日潛逃風險大增為由 拒被告保釋等候上訴","createTime":"2020-12-18T04:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T18:27:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6099eaa91ee061c084bd6898cfafe3a63c45898c","tid":2330425,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:26:30.000Z","msg":"大專生被指去年11月「營救理大」行動當日凌晨，在油麻地管有六角匙及剪鉗，早前被裁定管有物品意圖摧毀財產罪成，今日判刑。裁判官鄭念慈今指被告在求情信中表明甘願接受法庭判處的刑罰，惟被告不認罪，悔意有限，最終判被告進入更生中心。辯方為被告申請保釋等候上訴，鄭官以被告在警方擔保期間干犯本案、加上近日棄保潛逃風險大增為由，駁回保釋申請。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官鄭念慈今引述被告自撰的求情信指，被告表明願意接受法庭所有處罰，惟被告不認罪，法庭只能接受他僅有一定悔意。鄭官又引述報告指，被告身體狀況不適宜判入勞教所，考慮到案件性質及案情，最終接納報告建議，判被告入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n辯方申請保釋等候上訴，鄭念慈聞言謂：「嘩！寫封信畀我，就話接受所有處罰。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/R4OXDUVJZ5G53OMU7YJ4O44DIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FR4OXDUVJZ5G53OMU7YJ4O44DIY%2F&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrUlZDiKRLpOq3%2FNqhGVOPOo%3D&h=0b2cc25c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201218%2FR4OXDUVJZ5G53OMU7YJ4O44DIY%2F&h=e7810b0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201218/R4OXDUVJZ5G53OMU7YJ4O44DIY/</a>"},{"pid":"b64fa6583be1b74688569bd664962929c07be8f4","tid":2330425,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf71fc1db58bcfa387c31c07f8c1099942eafd0","tid":2330425,"uid":40520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:31:44.000Z","msg":"大律師公會:請相信法庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf45767aeba42d9d93a9c5b3185c808772e6d64","tid":2330425,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202